Overview of all Tracks commands
Commands: .fm · np | Shows you or someone else their current track .recent · r | Shows you or someone else their recent tracks .track · tr | Track you're currently listening to or searching for. .trackplays · tp | Shows playcount for current track or the one you're searching for. .trackdetails · td | Shows metadata for current track or the one you're searching for. .love · l | Loves a track on Last.fm .unlove · ul | Removes the track you're currently listening to or searching for from your last.fm loved tracks. .loved · lt | Shows your Last.fm loved tracks. .scrobble · sb | Scrobbles a track on Last.fm. .toptracks · tt | Shows your or someone else's top tracks over a certain time period. .receipt · rcpt | Shows your track receipt.
